        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant must be a farmer.\n   1.  The applicant must be a resident of Gujarat.\n   1. The applicant must plan to construct a cemented water storage tank of at least 25.50 cubic meters capacity.\n\n&gt; **Note:** Cemented mature water tanks, drip set mandatory.\n\n",
